<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA8">
<l>neyyiṭai nallatōr cōṟum niyatamu mattāṇic cēvakamum</l>
<l>kaiyaṭaik kāyum kaḻuttukkup pūṇoṭu kātukkuk kuṇṭalamum</l>
<l>meyyiṭa nallatōr cāntamum tanteṉṉai veḷḷuyi rākkavalla</l>
<l>paiyuṭai nākap pakaikkoṭi yāṉukkup pallāṇṭu kūṟuvēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[He] gave to me good boiled rice in ghee, restraint, service of [His] chamber,</l>
<l>Areca nut[for my] hands, gold-earring for [my] ears along with ornaments for [my] neck,</l>
<l>and good sandal on [my] body for the purpose of making my soul pure;</l>
<l>I proclaim “many years”</l>
<l rend="indent">for he who has a banner of the enemy of poweful snakes with hoods.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
